{
  "name": "TaskRelay — WhatsApp Task Router",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 1. Intake\nClient texts a task to the WhatsApp Business number. Meta's **Cloud API** delivers it to n8n as a webhook (subscribed to `messages`).\n\n**Edit Fields** normalizes any message type into:\n`client_phone` · `client_name` · `msg_type` · `text`\n\n`text` falls back to an image/video **caption**, so a photo or clip with the task in the caption still works.",
        "height": 527,
        "width": 539,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "f6970378-1d2a-4cc9-b60e-73bac65ebd20",
      "name": "Sticky · New message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -368,
        -160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2. Extract the task (AI)\n**gpt-4o-mini** turns free-form client chat into structured data.\n\nUses **Response Format = JSON Object** on the model plus a **Normalize** Code node — *not* the Structured Output Parser, which is unreliable on self-hosted n8n.\n\nOutput: `{ is_task, title, client, type, priority, summary }`\n\n`priority` is emitted as **High / Medium / Low** to match Monday's native labels exactly — no mapping code, no duplicate labels.",
        "height": 527,
        "width": 600,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "d230ed57-2244-40b8-baea-021694728e05",
      "name": "Sticky · Qualify (BANT agent)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        176,
        -160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 3. Is it actually a task?\nGates out chit-chat — \"thanks\", \"ok\", \"got it\" come back `is_task: false` and stop here.\n\nOnly real requests continue to Slack + Monday.",
        "height": 527,
        "width": 447,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "e4a23dce-dcdc-44d6-94e5-9bf50116bd1e",
      "name": "Sticky · Hot lead?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        784,
        -160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 4. Notify + file\n**Slack** — instant alert to the team channel.\n\n**Monday.com** — `create_item` via GraphQL (HTTP Request + Header Auth), mapped to the board's real column IDs.\n\nBoth hang off the IF's `true` output: the task is announced *and* filed.",
        "height": 527,
        "width": 281,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "2614f902-35f9-4b26-8195-891612678efc",
      "name": "Sticky · Alert sales",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1232,
        -160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": {
          "__rl": true,
